content:
Enable Workforce Engagement and Feature Preferences

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

To use Workforce Engagement, turn on the Workforce Engagement org preference and choose your data model. Configure preferences to let your planners and analysts use the configuration app and view adherence metrics.

Turn on the Workforce Engagement org preference:
From Setup, enter Workforce Engagement Management, and select Getting Started.
Click Enable.
Select your preferred data model, and click Next.

Enable the Workforce Engagement Configuration app:
From Setup, enter Workforce Engagement Management, and select Getting Started.
Select the Enable Workforce Engagement Configuration checkbox.

Turn on adherence metrics and set agent adherence data visibility:
Under Adherence, enable Show historical adherence metrics.
Optionally, select Include agent adherence data.
title: Enabling Workforce Engagement in Service Cloud
